data.description: Welcome to a haven of comfort and style in this 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home nestled in a serene subdivision. The inviting front porch sets the tone for a welcoming atmosphere, complemented by a low-maintenance lawn that ensures easy outdoor enjoyment. As you step through the front door, be prepared to be captivated by the custom accent designs that grace the walls of both the foyer and the primary bedroom. These unique touches add a touch of sophistication and character to the home, setting it apart from the ordinary.  The beautiful floor plan seamlessly connects each room, creating a harmonious flow throughout. The spacious secondary bedrooms offer comfort and versatility, providing the ideal space for family members, guests, or a home office. Culinary enthusiasts will appreciate the well-equipped kitchen featuring a 5-burner gas cooktop, a double oven, island, and gleaming hardwood floors on the main level. Whether you're hosting family gatherings or preparing everyday meals, this kitchen is designed for both convenience and style.  The primary bedroom offers a retreat within your own home, with ample space and a luxurious large shower and soaking tub for relaxation. Each detail thoroughly provides comfort and elegance.  This residence not only exudes charm but is also designed for practical living. With custom accents, premium features, and a thoughtful floor plan, this home is ready to be your sanctuary. Don't miss the chance to make this 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem your own.
